doc.after: Despite requests from Kansas City the airport has been unable to change its original International Air Transport Association IATA Mid Continent designation of MCI which had already been registered on navigational charts Further complicating requests to change the designation the Federal Communications Commission FCC at the time reserved all call letters with K or W for radio and television stations so KCI was not viable 29
